{"tid":2506222,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"發展商又有新搞作！屯門新盤推特別限定版大富翁 地價最貴變瑧譽","createTime":"2021-04-27T07:17:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T08:18:37.000Z","uid":166360,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"c8dec532569f342c21b0a355d55a1195a80d9ebe","tid":2506222,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T07:17:10.000Z","msg":"發展商又有新搞作！屯門新盤推特別限定版大富翁 地價最貴變瑧譽<br />\n14:10 2021/04/27<br />\n<br />\n&quot;......保利置業﹙香港﹚與Monopoly﹙大富翁﹚英國發行商 Winning Moves UK Limited 合作，製作屯門瑧譽尊屬限量版大富翁......<br />\n<br />\n......普通版地價最貴的太平山/山頂，變成了瑧譽；地價較平的長洲、梅窩等地，則變成了港珠澳大橋、青馬大橋等地標。<br />\n<br />\n保利置業(香港)銷售及市務部總監朱美儀表示此批瑧譽尊屬限量版大富翁，只饋贈予賣方貴賓及瑧譽買家......&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2942478/%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%8F%88%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E6%90%9E%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%81%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E7%89%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%8C%E7%BF%81%20%E5%9C%B0%E5%83%B9%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B4%E8%AE%8A%E7%91%A7%E8%AD%BD?mtc=60037\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2942478%2F%25E7%2599%25BC%25E5%25B1%2595%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%258F%2588%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%2596%25B0%25E6%2590%259E%25E4%25BD%259C%25EF%25BC%2581%25E5%25B1%25AF%25E9%2596%2580%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%259B%25A4%25E6%258E%25A8%25E7%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%25A5%25E9%2599%2590%25E5%25AE%259A%25E7%2589%2588%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25AF%258C%25E7%25BF%2581%2520%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%259C%2580%25E8%25B2%25B4%25E8%25AE%258A%25E7%2591%25A7%25E8%25AD%25BD%3Fmtc%3D60037&d=1Ie%2FqJFF6iBMyzR%2B2a49oFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=4918101a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2942478/%E7%99%BC%E5%B1%95%E5%95%86%E5%8F%88%E6%9C%89%E6%96%B0%E6%90%9E%E4%BD%9C%EF%BC%81%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E6%96%B0%E7%9B%A4%E6%8E%A8%E7%89%B9%E5%88%A5%E9%99%90%E5%AE%9A%E7%89%88%E5%A4%A7%E5%AF%8C%E7%BF%81%20%E5%9C%B0%E5%83%B9%E6%9C%80%E8%B2%B4%E8%AE%8A%E7%91%A7%E8%AD%BD?mtc=60037</a><br />\